\c 10
\p
\v 1 Nhamo kune vanotema mitemo yezvakaipa, nekuvanyoro vanonyora matambudziko;
\v 2 kutsausa varombo pamutongo, nekutora nechisimba mutongo wevarombo vevanhu vangu, kuti chirikadzi vave vakapambiwa vavo, kuti vapambe nherera.
\v 3 Asi muchaitei pazuva retsivo, nepakuparara kuchabva kure? Muchatizira kuna ani kurubatsiro? Muchasiyepi rukudzo rwenyu?
\v 4 Kunze kwangu vachakotama pasi pevasungwa, uye vachawira pasi pevakaurawa. Pane zvese izvi, kutsamwa kwake hakungadzirwi, ruoko rwake rwakangotandavadzwa.
\s Kurohwa kwevaAsiriya
\p
\v 5 Nhamo kumuAsiriya, mudonzvo wekutsamwa kwangu, uye hasha dzangu itsvimbo muruoko rwavo!
\v 6 Ndichamutumira rudzi rwunonyepedzera, ndichamuraira kurwisa vanhu vehasha dzangu, kutora zvakapambiwa nekutora zvakatapiwa, nekuvatsikira pasi sedope riri munzira dzemumusha.
\v 7 Asi iye haafungi saizvozvo, nemoyo wake haurangariri zvakadaro; asi zviri mumoyo wake kuparadza, nekugura marudzi asiri mashoma.
\v 8 Nokuti anoti: Machinda angu ese haasi madzimambo here?
\v 9 Karino harina kuita seKarikemishi here? Hamati harina kuita seAripadhi here? Samariya haina kuita seDhamasiko here?
\v 10 Ruoko rwangu sezvarwakawana ushe hwezvifananidzo, zvifananidzo zvahwo zvakavezwa zvai\add chipfuura\add* zvepaJerusarema nezveSamariya.
\v 11 Sezvandakaitira Samariya nezvifananidzo zvayo, handingaitiri Jerusarema nezvifananidzo zvaro here?
\p
\v 12 Zvino zvakaitika, Jehovha apedza basa rake rese pagomo reZiyoni muJerusarema,, ndichatsiva chibereko chekuzvikudza kwemoyo wamambo weAsiriya, nekunaka kwemanyawi emeso ake.
\v 13 Nokuti wakati: Ndakazviita nesimba reruoko rwangu, uye neuchenjeri hwangu, nokuti ndine njere; uye ndakabvisa miganhu yemarudzi, uye ndakapamba fuma yavo, uye seane simba ndakawisira pasi vagari vawo.
\v 14 ruoko rwangu rwakawana fuma yamarudzi avanhu sedendere; ndakaunganidza nyika yese, somunhu anounganidza mazai akasiiwa; hapana akapfakanyisa bapiro, kana kushamisa muromo, kana kurira.
\v 15 Ko sanhu ringazvirumbidza pamusoro poanotema naro here? Kana jeko ringazvikudza pamusoro paanobata naro here? Zvaifanana netsvimbo inozunungusa vanorova nayo, kana mudonzvo unosimudza chinhu chisati chiri huni.
\v 16 Naizvozvo Ishe, Ishe wehondo, achatuma kuonda pakati pavakakora vake; pasi pokubwinya kwake pachabatidzwa chinopisa chakafanana nokupisa komoto.
\v 17 Chiedza chaVaIsraeri chichava moto, noMutsvene wake murazvo womoto; uchapisa nokupedza minzwa yake norukato rwake nezuva rimwe.
\v 18 Uchapedza kubwinya kwedondo rake, nokomunda wake wakaorera, mweya nomuviri kamwe, zvifanane nendonda inongoramba ichipera simba.
\v 19 Miti yakasara yedondo rake ichava mishoma, inganyorwa nomwana.
\p
\v 20 Zvino nezuva iro vakasara VaIsraeri, navanenge vapukunyuka paimba yaJakove, havangazosendamiri kunowakavarova, asi vachasendamira kuna Jehovha, Mutsvene waIsraeri, nezvokwadi.
\v 21 Vakasara vachadzoka, ivo vakasara vaJakove, kuna Mwari ane simba.
\v 22 Nokuti kunyange vanhu venyu, imwi Israeri, vakaita sejecha regungwa, vakasara vavo vega vachadzoka; nokuti vakatemerwa kuparadzwa kuzere nokururama.
\v 23 Nokuti Ishe, Jehovha wehondo, achapedzisa kuparadza, kwakagara kwatemwa, panyika yese.
\v 24 Saka zvanzi nashe, Jehovha wehondo: Imi vanhu vangu vagere Ziyoni, musatya muAsiriya, kunyange akakurovai neshamhu nokukusimudzirai tsvimbo yake, sezvaakaitira Egipita.
\v 25 Nokuti kwasara chinguva chidiki, kutsamwa kwangu kuchapera, hasha dzangu dzichavaparadza.
\v 26 Jehovha wehondo achamusimudzira tyava, sapakurohwa kwaVaMidhiani padombo reOrebhi; shamhu yake ichava pamusoro pegungwa, achaisimudza sezvaakaitira Egipita.
\v 27 Zvino nezuva iro mutoro wake uchabviswa pamafudzi ako, nejoko rake pamutsipa wako, joko richaparadzwa nokuda kwamafuta.
\p
\v 28 Asvika paAiati, apfuura napaMigironi, achengeta nhumbi dzake paMikimashi;
\v 29 vakwira napamupata, vakarara paGebha usiku; Rama rinodedera, Gibhiya raSauro ratiza.
\v 30 Danidzira nenzwi rako, iwe mukunda weGarimi! Teerera, iwe Raishi! Iwe Anatoti wourombo!
\v 31 Madhimena wotiza, vagere Ghebhimi vorongedza kutiza.
\v 32 Zuva ranhasi achazorota paNobhi; anozunungusira gomo romukunda weZiyoni, icho chikomo cheJerusarema, ruoko rwake.
\v 33 Tarirai, Ishe, Jehovha wehondo, achatema mashizha nokutyisa; akareba achatemwa, naakakwirira achawiswa pasi.
\v 34 Achatema nedare matenhere edondo, Rebhanoni richawiswa neane simba.
